title: HMSI domestic overall sales rise 42 pc to 4,19,395 units in January
description: Honda Motorcycle & Scooter India (HMSI) Pvt Ltd had dispatched a total of 2,96,375 units to the market in January 2023, according to a statement. Of the total sales, domestic volumes rose 37 per cent to 3,82,512 units in January from 2,78,155 vehicles in the year-ago period, HMSI said. Exports grew a whopping 102 per cent year-on-year at 36,883 units in the previous month, it stated.
